    {
      "chinese": "所有葛蕾扇流域的部落都是沿著南湖大山的周圍山嶺而生活。過去葛蕾扇流域的部落計有Kngyan、Babollaw、Rekax、Hagaparis、Tubulak、Pyahaw、Tlangan、Tpyaxan、Gogo、Rkinus、Ryohen和Moyaw。所有部落飲用的水源，要狩獵的山產，要耕作的田地，都是從南湖大山週邊的山嶺而來。",
      "ab": "kwara alang cyu maki llyung Mklesan ga nyu siy pgluw m’yanux llingay rrgyax na Rgyax B’bu Topok. lela ku kwara alang na llyung Mklesan ga, maki Kngyan, Babollaw, Rekax, Hagaparis, Tubulak, Pyahaw, Tlangan, Tpyaxan, Gogo, Rkinus, Ryohen ru Moyaw. kwara ka pu’ing ’sya ni’ung alang, kwara ka ksinu halan naha mluyak, kwara ka pmahan ta mayah ga, mnkahun sku llingay rrgyax na Rgyax B’bu Topok kwara.",
